WEBVTT

02:35.180 --> 02:36.699
You said you were going to disappear.

02:36.699 --> 02:38.100
Did you mean running away to Shen'ao?

02:39.060 --> 02:39.739
Yeah.

02:40.340 --> 02:41.180
In Hangzhou,

02:41.180 --> 02:42.500
I can run into him anywhere.

02:43.819 --> 02:45.419
I had to disappear for a while.

02:46.019 --> 02:46.419
Did you see

02:46.419 --> 02:47.380
the photos I sent you?

02:48.299 --> 02:49.739
Shen'ao is really beautiful.

02:50.180 --> 02:51.900
Maybe this trip to gather inspiration

02:52.340 --> 02:53.620
will actually lead to new ideas.

02:56.940 --> 02:58.819
Alright, good luck with your trip.

02:59.019 --> 03:01.139
[I'll wait for your return in Hangzhou.]

03:04.940 --> 03:07.100
[I've already made contact with Mr. Zhang.]

03:07.380 --> 03:09.340
[Please wait for good news.]

03:17.699 --> 03:18.460
Lawyer?

03:19.139 --> 03:19.620
Yes.

03:21.500 --> 03:23.060
She even hired a lawyer.

03:24.299 --> 03:25.060
Where is she?

03:25.180 --> 03:26.340
I'm looking for my girlfriend,

03:26.340 --> 03:27.019
not you.

03:27.699 --> 03:28.220
Well,

03:28.220 --> 03:28.900
I'm now

03:28.900 --> 03:30.460
Miss Shen's attorney.

03:30.660 --> 03:31.139
If you have any questions,

03:31.139 --> 03:31.979
you can discuss them with me first.

03:32.259 --> 03:33.900
How can I discuss it with you?

03:34.660 --> 03:36.180
This is a personal matter between us.

03:37.100 --> 03:37.620
Fine.

03:38.460 --> 03:39.460
Even if she has appointed you

03:39.460 --> 03:40.340
to handle the lawsuit against me,

03:40.940 --> 03:42.340
what exactly does she intend to sue me for?

03:42.660 --> 03:43.340
It's quite simple.

03:43.819 --> 03:45.139
My client's current claim

03:45.139 --> 03:45.780
is to retrieve the expenses

03:45.780 --> 03:47.220
incurred during your relationship.

03:47.539 --> 03:48.380
During your relationship,

03:48.380 --> 03:49.180
the substantial gifts

03:49.180 --> 03:49.940
she gave you

03:49.940 --> 03:51.259
were intended for marriage.

03:51.660 --> 03:52.699
So, she has the right

03:52.819 --> 03:53.579
to ask for their return.

03:53.859 --> 03:54.539
Wait,

03:54.539 --> 03:56.139
I never said I wouldn't marry her.

03:56.620 --> 03:58.539
It's her who insisted on breaking up.

03:59.139 --> 03:59.660
And those gifts

03:59.660 --> 04:00.660
were given willingly.

04:01.460 --> 04:02.579
Whether they were given willingly

04:02.579 --> 04:03.660
isn't something you can decide.

04:04.060 --> 04:04.979
I have

04:04.979 --> 04:06.340
screenshot of our WeChat chat

04:06.340 --> 04:07.259
as evidence.

04:07.259 --> 04:09.340
It proves that during your relationship,

04:09.859 --> 04:10.699
you used

04:10.819 --> 04:11.819
the excuse that marrying

04:11.819 --> 04:13.579
would make things better

04:13.579 --> 04:14.660
to repeatedly

04:15.139 --> 04:16.460
ask her for money.

04:17.139 --> 04:18.579
But cheating

04:18.579 --> 04:19.299
during a relationship

04:19.500 --> 04:20.180
you've already

04:20.180 --> 04:21.259
crossed the moral line.

04:21.500 --> 04:21.979
No.

04:22.180 --> 04:24.220
Cheating in a relationship

04:24.619 --> 04:26.580
isn't illegal, is it?

04:27.260 --> 04:28.900
And it's all men.

04:28.900 --> 04:31.299
You understand a little slip, right?

04:31.460 --> 04:32.539
Sorry, Mr. Zhang.

04:33.780 --> 04:34.820
Even though I'm a man,

04:35.820 --> 04:36.979
I can't agree with

04:36.979 --> 04:37.939
your statement.

04:40.419 --> 04:41.419
There are

04:41.780 --> 04:42.619
there are many men

04:42.619 --> 04:43.580
who are not like you.

04:44.299 --> 04:45.260
I believe a man

04:45.939 --> 04:47.379
should be loyal,

04:47.939 --> 04:48.580
faithful,

04:48.939 --> 04:49.859
responsible,

04:50.220 --> 04:51.419
and respectful of boundaries.

04:53.140 --> 04:54.739
Are you trying to act, buddy?

04:55.419 --> 04:56.419
Have you ever been in a relationship?

04:57.140 --> 04:57.900
Are you married?

04:58.419 --> 04:59.859
How long was your longest relationship?

05:00.539 --> 05:02.460
Do you know how suffocating it is

05:02.460 --> 05:03.100
and you see her every day,

05:03.100 --> 05:04.619
and she changes every day,

05:04.619 --> 05:05.700
how suffocating is that?

05:06.140 --> 05:07.220
And then suddenly,

05:07.220 --> 05:08.299
someone new appears,

05:08.580 --> 05:10.100
shining bright,

05:10.499 --> 05:11.499
and helping you

05:11.499 --> 05:12.299
with your career.

05:12.820 --> 05:13.979
You'd be tempted too.

05:13.979 --> 05:15.379
But your girlfriend, sorry,

05:15.780 --> 05:16.739
your ex-girlfriend,

05:16.739 --> 05:18.020
when she was in your life,

05:18.499 --> 05:19.820
wasn't she also shining?

05:20.059 --> 05:22.299
But that was five years ago, bro.

05:22.619 --> 05:24.140
What light does she have on her face now?

05:24.140 --> 05:25.539
That's your eyes having a problem.

05:25.539 --> 05:26.499
There's no light in your eyes anymore,

05:26.499 --> 05:27.539
so you can't see anything.

05:27.539 --> 05:28.379
That's your problem.

05:28.379 --> 05:30.020
How did it come back to me?

05:30.020 --> 05:30.660
I said,

05:30.660 --> 05:32.460
now it's her who insists on breaking up.

05:33.260 --> 05:34.419
You should go and persuade her.

05:34.419 --> 05:35.299
What should I persuade her of?

05:35.700 --> 05:36.499
To recycle trash?

05:36.499 --> 05:37.619
Who are you calling trash?

05:37.979 --> 05:38.900
Do you know how I've lived

05:38.900 --> 05:39.619
these past five years?

05:39.979 --> 05:41.979
I cooked, cleaned,

05:41.979 --> 05:43.260
even gave her foot baths.

05:43.379 --> 05:44.100
I took care of her

05:44.100 --> 05:45.020
so well.

05:45.140 --> 05:46.660
Now that she's without me,

05:46.939 --> 05:48.140
who would want

05:48.140 --> 05:49.020
that old face of hers?

05:49.020 --> 05:49.660
Zhang Chuan,

05:54.140 --> 05:54.580
Baby.

05:57.020 --> 05:58.100
Lawyer Liu is right.

05:58.100 --> 05:59.260
You are a piece of trash.

05:59.379 --> 06:00.660
My love for you

06:00.660 --> 06:02.059
made you look less disgusting.

06:02.179 --> 06:02.979
I'm telling you,

06:03.140 --> 06:05.220
don't worry about my age.

06:05.859 --> 06:07.020
No matter how old I get,

06:07.020 --> 06:07.660
I will never

06:07.660 --> 06:09.020
look for a man in the trash again.

06:09.419 --> 06:09.939
And,

06:10.220 --> 06:11.660
if you think age is an issue,

06:12.260 --> 06:14.059
I think every year I get older,

06:14.340 --> 06:15.739
every bit of experience I gain,

06:15.979 --> 06:17.299
every bit of knowledge I acquire,

06:17.379 --> 06:18.340
is my strength to stay away from you,

06:18.340 --> 06:19.859
this kind of trash.

06:21.460 --> 06:23.260
Trash is also divided into different categories.

06:24.059 --> 06:24.900
Your kind

06:26.020 --> 06:28.979
is considered cheap even among trash.

06:37.299 --> 06:38.020
Are you okay?

06:38.460 --> 06:39.059
I'm fine.

06:39.820 --> 06:40.939
Just my hand hurts a bit.

06:43.020 --> 06:44.299
Don't take too seriously

06:45.059 --> 06:45.939
what he said.

06:46.299 --> 06:47.059
I won't.

06:47.460 --> 06:48.059
Trash

06:48.059 --> 06:49.020
only deserves to be thrown in the trash can,

06:49.020 --> 06:50.220
not worth bothering my mind.

06:53.379 --> 06:55.700
I think you're great and excellent.

06:57.140 --> 06:57.780
Thank you.

06:58.499 --> 06:59.140
I know.

07:01.539 --> 07:02.340
And just now...

07:03.299 --> 07:03.820
Thanks.

07:04.260 --> 07:05.179
It's what I should do.

07:05.619 --> 07:06.979
About the expenses you want to recover,

07:07.020 --> 07:07.660
don't worry,

07:07.780 --> 07:08.700
I'll keep on it.

07:08.700 --> 07:09.100
Good.

07:11.100 --> 07:11.859
Where are you going? I'll give you a ride.

07:12.379 --> 07:12.820
No need.

07:13.939 --> 07:15.059
After dealing with the romantic battle,

07:15.059 --> 07:16.499
it's time to tackle the work battle.

07:16.820 --> 07:17.340
Right.

07:17.660 --> 07:19.100
Don't tell Ruan Yu about this yet.

07:19.619 --> 07:20.780
She's been busy enough lately.

07:20.820 --> 07:21.460
Okay.

07:35.859 --> 07:36.379
Miss,

07:37.340 --> 07:38.100
just arrived, right?

07:38.859 --> 07:40.020
Still looking for a place to stay?

07:41.100 --> 07:42.260
Come check out our guesthouse.

07:42.619 --> 07:43.780
I'm sure you'll like it.

07:44.220 --> 07:45.100
Come, I'll show you.

07:46.260 --> 07:46.739
Let's go.

07:46.900 --> 07:48.140
Sis, I can manage on my own.

07:48.379 --> 07:49.820
Don't be shy, we're all family here.

07:50.619 --> 07:51.020
Okay.

07:51.379 --> 07:53.580
We're like family from all over the world.

07:54.419 --> 07:55.539
First time in Shen'ao, right?

07:56.179 --> 07:57.419
You've come to the right place.

07:57.419 --> 07:58.059
Look,

07:58.340 --> 07:59.580
how beautiful it is here.

08:00.539 --> 08:02.460
Not only the place is beautiful, but the people are also beautiful.

08:02.700 --> 08:03.499
It's quite beautiful.

08:03.499 --> 08:04.780
The main thing is the enthusiasm.

08:06.539 --> 08:07.580
Give me your phone.

08:07.780 --> 08:08.979
If you have any problems, just talk.

08:09.140 --> 08:10.059
If you don't give me the money,

08:10.220 --> 08:11.340
you can't leave this village.

08:11.340 --> 08:12.260
Don't fight. Just talk.

08:12.299 --> 08:13.900
They must have some misunderstanding.

08:14.700 --> 08:15.580
Don't worry.

08:15.580 --> 08:16.780
Sis, I've changed my mind.

08:16.780 --> 08:18.179
I don't want to stay in a homestay.

08:18.619 --> 08:19.179
Maybe next time.

08:19.460 --> 08:20.260
But you haven't

08:20.260 --> 08:21.059
even checked it out yet.

08:21.059 --> 08:21.619
You don't know

08:21.619 --> 08:22.780
if you like it or not.

08:22.780 --> 08:24.100
No, no, go check it out first.

08:24.100 --> 08:25.140
You haven't seen it yet.

08:25.140 --> 08:26.179
Go check it out, at least take a look.

08:26.179 --> 08:27.299
I'll pass for now.

08:27.419 --> 08:28.340
Give me your suitcase.

08:28.340 --> 08:30.220
Girl, give me the suitcase.

08:36.379 --> 08:37.499
Give me the suitcase.

08:41.259 --> 08:41.979
Ouch.

08:42.420 --> 08:43.340
Hold on.

08:43.779 --> 08:44.940
It works.

08:47.300 --> 08:48.540
Sorry, Uncle Wang.

08:49.700 --> 08:50.619
I thought...

08:50.779 --> 08:51.739
It's not your fault.

08:52.139 --> 08:52.979
It's my fault.

08:53.460 --> 08:54.420
He's too fierce.

08:54.420 --> 08:56.019
Any girl would be scared.

08:57.379 --> 08:58.340
Don't move.

09:00.139 --> 09:01.659
It's not your fault.

09:02.379 --> 09:04.019
Who are those two people?

09:04.340 --> 09:04.940
You don't know.

09:04.940 --> 09:06.379
They are selling health products.

09:06.619 --> 09:07.460
Every time they come,

09:07.460 --> 09:09.139
they shout free eggs.

09:09.139 --> 09:09.619
Yes.

09:09.979 --> 09:11.060
They are good at cheating the elderly.

09:11.739 --> 09:12.859
This time,

09:12.859 --> 09:13.619
they cheated away several thousand yuan from Old Li.

09:13.619 --> 09:14.420
Yes.

09:14.820 --> 09:15.460
It's not easy for the elderly

09:15.460 --> 09:16.739
for them to save up a few thousand.

09:16.739 --> 09:17.220
Yeah.

09:17.420 --> 09:19.060
Luckily, I ran into them

09:19.220 --> 09:20.180
and got the money back.

09:20.420 --> 09:21.019
Yes.

09:21.180 --> 09:22.379
I'm sorry, Uncle Wang.

09:22.379 --> 09:23.420
I misunderstood you.

09:24.100 --> 09:25.019
It's okay.

09:25.340 --> 09:26.220
But, girl,

09:26.379 --> 09:28.619
you've got quite the grip.

09:30.979 --> 09:32.180
That's good.

09:34.940 --> 09:36.499
It'll keep you safe out there.

09:37.659 --> 09:38.899
By the way, Miss Ruan,

09:38.899 --> 09:39.619
let me tell you,

09:40.060 --> 09:41.139
my guesthouse

09:41.460 --> 09:42.499
is quite unique.

09:43.460 --> 09:44.420
It's fully equipped,

09:44.420 --> 09:45.220
and has everything you need.

09:45.700 --> 09:46.460
So, if you need anything,

09:46.580 --> 09:47.820
just let me know.

09:47.820 --> 09:49.180
Don't be shy.

09:49.180 --> 09:49.820
Thank you, Ms. Cai.

09:51.019 --> 09:51.540
No problem.

09:52.300 --> 09:53.820
Later, apply some of Mr. Li's

09:53.820 --> 09:55.300
after a while.

09:55.659 --> 09:56.619
You are so troublesome.

09:56.619 --> 09:58.139
Then eat this egg.

09:58.139 --> 09:59.139
What a waste.

10:00.139 --> 10:00.659
Well,

10:00.739 --> 10:01.739
I'll take Mr. Wang back.

10:01.739 --> 10:02.899
Okay, we're leaving. Take care.

10:40.220 --> 10:41.139
How are you?

10:56.619 --> 10:58.379
These are some places

10:58.379 --> 10:59.540
we've chosen this year.

10:59.700 --> 11:00.619
As you know,

11:00.619 --> 11:01.540
it's our rule

11:01.540 --> 11:02.940
We spend some time every year

11:02.940 --> 11:03.820
doing public welfare.

11:04.420 --> 11:06.100
This time, we're going to provide

11:06.580 --> 11:07.340
legal services

11:07.340 --> 11:09.100
for the local residents.

11:12.100 --> 11:13.060
Isn't anyone interested?

11:19.859 --> 11:21.220
I went last year.

11:22.460 --> 11:23.460
This year, I'm really

11:23.460 --> 11:24.700
unable to do it.

11:25.019 --> 11:26.619
My child is in the third year of high school. I'm stressed.

11:27.340 --> 11:28.619
I understand.

11:31.820 --> 11:32.340
Mao, I...

11:32.340 --> 11:33.820
I have too many cases on hand.

11:33.820 --> 11:35.180
I'm so busy.

11:36.499 --> 11:38.139
So busy.

11:43.499 --> 11:45.139
Shen'ao Ancient Town

11:46.060 --> 11:46.739
is a nice place.

11:47.100 --> 11:48.580
Although it hasn't been fully developed,

11:48.580 --> 11:49.739
the local customs

11:49.739 --> 11:50.619
are very simple and honest.

11:53.180 --> 11:54.540
Are you interested in

11:55.940 --> 11:56.499
public welfare?

11:56.499 --> 11:57.820
I often do it in the United States.

11:58.340 --> 11:58.940
But I don't have

11:58.940 --> 12:00.340
a domestic lawyer's license.

12:00.739 --> 12:01.540
And I also have to

12:01.540 --> 12:02.340
push forward the case in the US.

12:04.379 --> 12:05.379
In that case,

12:15.100 --> 12:15.580
is this also

12:15.580 --> 12:16.739
Shen'ao Ancient Town?

12:22.019 --> 12:22.739
What a coincidence.

12:32.220 --> 12:33.139
I remember you have a court trial

12:33.139 --> 12:34.300
at the beginning of the month.

12:35.019 --> 12:35.820
Public welfare is important,

12:35.940 --> 12:37.139
but your client is

12:37.139 --> 12:38.019
also very important.

12:38.100 --> 12:38.619
Yes.

12:39.979 --> 12:40.739
I'll go.

12:43.340 --> 12:43.940
You go.

12:44.460 --> 12:44.979
I'll go.

12:45.739 --> 12:47.259
Then don't you need to

12:47.259 --> 12:48.100
push forward your business in the US?

12:50.379 --> 12:51.100
I can handle it.

12:51.499 --> 12:52.420
You don't have to, right?

12:52.420 --> 12:53.420
Of course not.

12:53.779 --> 12:54.700
But you don't have a lawyer's license.

12:56.019 --> 12:57.220
You are so capable.

12:57.220 --> 12:58.379
It doesn't matter.

12:58.619 --> 12:59.540
Just find a lawyer with a license

12:59.540 --> 13:00.979
to go with you.

13:01.259 --> 13:02.139
Then you go.

13:03.340 --> 13:04.619
You're so easy-going.

13:05.899 --> 13:06.379
I...

13:06.379 --> 13:07.580
I'm busy as a bee.

13:07.820 --> 13:08.820
It doesn't matter.

13:11.100 --> 13:11.580
I...

13:19.139 --> 13:19.940
Lawyer Xu,

13:20.300 --> 13:21.420
the road here is paved with stone slabs.

13:21.420 --> 13:23.139
Your shoes will be ruined.

13:26.019 --> 13:27.180
Since we're here, just accept it.

13:27.460 --> 13:28.739
We can't slack off

13:28.820 --> 13:30.100
even if it's for charity.

13:31.379 --> 13:31.940
Alright.

13:32.499 --> 13:33.499
Let's go over there.

13:36.180 --> 13:37.499
What if no one

13:37.499 --> 13:38.420
comes to us?

13:44.180 --> 13:45.340
No one can refuse

13:45.340 --> 13:46.540
something for free.

13:47.859 --> 13:49.540
These free eggs

13:49.979 --> 13:50.700
are the key

13:50.700 --> 13:52.220
to unlocking people's hearts.

13:54.100 --> 13:56.139
These inspiring words

13:56.499 --> 13:58.739
build the bridge of communication.

14:04.540 --> 14:06.540
Will it work?

14:06.619 --> 14:07.979
Of course.

14:08.940 --> 14:09.700
At first,

14:09.700 --> 14:11.460
they are attracted by the free eggs.

14:12.259 --> 14:13.460
But after getting the eggs,

14:13.739 --> 14:14.779
they will be trapped.

14:15.100 --> 14:16.100
Then they will be

14:16.100 --> 14:17.499
sold health products.

14:18.300 --> 14:20.019
Especially the old people.

14:20.300 --> 14:20.859
These old people

14:20.859 --> 14:22.139
have a generation gap with us.

14:22.700 --> 14:23.700
and don't trust us,

14:24.139 --> 14:25.899
but when we give them

14:25.899 --> 14:27.820
these free eggs,

14:28.019 --> 14:29.100
they will open their hearts

14:29.100 --> 14:30.100
to us

14:31.379 --> 14:32.060
and feel

14:32.060 --> 14:33.739
our warmth like family.

14:34.019 --> 14:35.019
Warmth my foot.

14:36.340 --> 14:38.100
They're too bad.

14:39.060 --> 14:40.379
They say they're bringing warmth,

14:40.379 --> 14:41.659
but they're really just

14:41.659 --> 14:42.859
after the old folks' money.

14:45.060 --> 14:46.259
What if they come again,

14:46.259 --> 14:47.019
what should we do?

14:47.220 --> 14:48.019
They dare to come again?

14:49.379 --> 14:50.739
I'll beat them every time they come.

14:55.379 --> 14:57.540
Lawyer Xu, is your hand okay?

14:58.460 --> 14:59.019
It's okay.

15:00.739 --> 15:01.499
Just a little blood.

15:03.139 --> 15:05.060
It's bleeding before we start.

15:05.540 --> 15:06.300
Lawyer Xu,

15:07.379 --> 15:08.100
will we

15:08.100 --> 15:09.940
have a disaster today?

15:27.940 --> 15:29.580
Lawyer Xu, I...

15:30.220 --> 15:31.700
Shall we go back?

15:32.899 --> 15:33.619
Go back?

15:34.739 --> 15:36.820
That's where we'll get hurt.

15:41.940 --> 15:42.619
Auntie.

15:43.499 --> 15:44.060
Auntie.

15:44.379 --> 15:44.940
Egg.

15:45.379 --> 15:47.220
Someone is handing out free eggs

15:47.220 --> 15:48.460
with banners in the square.

15:49.899 --> 15:51.340
They dare to come again after being beaten.

15:51.340 --> 15:52.460
How bold!

15:52.460 --> 15:53.180
Damn it!

15:53.379 --> 15:54.499
Come on, sister.

15:54.619 --> 15:55.779
Let's calm down first.

15:56.060 --> 15:57.540
What if it's not that group

15:57.540 --> 15:58.820
of health product salespeople?

15:59.420 --> 16:00.220
You don't know.

16:00.739 --> 16:01.580
Let me tell you,

16:02.060 --> 16:03.259
ironclad suit,

16:03.379 --> 16:04.460
free eggs,

16:04.899 --> 16:06.220
eye-catching identity,

16:06.499 --> 16:07.460
and slick talk.

16:07.580 --> 16:08.739
As long as these four conditions are met,

16:08.940 --> 16:09.700
it's definitely

16:09.700 --> 16:11.859
a health product scammer.

16:12.420 --> 16:14.220
So what is the eye-catching identity

16:14.220 --> 16:15.820
and the set phrases?

16:15.979 --> 16:17.180
They won't tell us

16:17.180 --> 16:18.619
they are selling health products.

16:19.259 --> 16:20.779
They always say they are

16:20.859 --> 16:22.420
doctors, teachers,

16:22.940 --> 16:24.220
or even university professors.

16:24.420 --> 16:25.379
They have a good identity.

16:25.379 --> 16:26.100
As for the set phrases,

16:26.580 --> 16:27.659
they are just

16:27.659 --> 16:29.820
a few lines repeated over and over again.

16:30.379 --> 16:31.100
Like

16:32.060 --> 16:34.220
we are family,

16:34.220 --> 16:35.899
feel free to

16:35.899 --> 16:37.420
reach out to us,

16:37.420 --> 16:39.060
we're here to help.

16:39.540 --> 16:40.180
That's all.

16:41.379 --> 16:42.180
Tell me, Dandan,

16:42.420 --> 16:43.820
were they wearing suits?

16:43.820 --> 16:44.499
Yes.

16:44.739 --> 16:46.220
See? I told you.

16:46.300 --> 16:46.739
Go.

16:58.220 --> 16:59.340
Look, someone's coming.

17:01.739 --> 17:03.619
Feels like trouble.

17:06.739 --> 17:07.300
Hello.

17:07.499 --> 17:08.139
Here you are.

17:11.060 --> 17:12.340
You look pretty handsome.

17:14.300 --> 17:15.980
The suit looks good.

17:16.619 --> 17:17.179
Thank you.

17:17.740 --> 17:18.859
Do you need any help?

17:19.740 --> 17:21.020
The eggs are all set up.

17:21.899 --> 17:22.419
Right.

17:22.419 --> 17:23.540
Everyone can take one.

17:25.619 --> 17:27.459
What are you two

17:27.459 --> 17:28.260
doing here?

17:28.899 --> 17:29.540
Well,

17:29.619 --> 17:30.780
we're lawyers,

17:30.780 --> 17:31.540
and we're just thinking...

17:33.260 --> 17:36.379
You've chosen a great profession this time.

17:36.820 --> 17:37.780
It's quite unique,

17:38.060 --> 17:39.659
different, and not cliché.

17:39.899 --> 17:40.899
Do you have your lawyer's license?

17:41.060 --> 17:42.500
I came from abroad,

17:42.500 --> 17:43.300
so my lawyer's license...

17:44.260 --> 17:44.780
Understood.

17:45.139 --> 17:45.699
He has it.

17:47.500 --> 17:48.740
What's wrong?

17:49.300 --> 17:50.020
What's the matter?

17:50.260 --> 17:52.060
Go on, keep talking.

17:52.060 --> 17:52.740
You don't have anything

17:52.740 --> 17:53.619
to tell us?

17:53.619 --> 17:54.260
Keep going.

17:54.260 --> 17:55.139
You help introduce.

17:55.139 --> 17:55.859
So proactive.

17:55.859 --> 17:56.379
Yes.

17:57.100 --> 17:58.260
We're here

17:58.260 --> 17:59.419
mainly for charity.

18:00.300 --> 18:00.820
If anyone has

18:00.820 --> 18:01.820
any legal questions,

18:01.820 --> 18:02.780
feel free to come to us.

18:03.100 --> 18:04.100
Don't be afraid to ask.

18:04.820 --> 18:05.540
Just think of us

18:05.540 --> 18:06.619
as family.

18:06.659 --> 18:07.139
Oh my!

18:07.580 --> 18:08.619
My goodness, it's all here.

18:10.060 --> 18:11.300
Everything matches up.

18:11.580 --> 18:13.300
Not a single discrepancy.

18:15.540 --> 18:16.379
If any of you have

18:16.379 --> 18:17.659
legal questions,

18:17.659 --> 18:18.540
feel free to ask me.

18:19.699 --> 18:20.699
What if it's not

18:20.699 --> 18:21.780
a legal issue?

18:21.780 --> 18:22.459
can you help us?

18:22.459 --> 18:22.899
Yes.

18:22.980 --> 18:23.859
As long as it's

18:23.859 --> 18:24.939
within our capabilities,

18:24.939 --> 18:25.899
we'll do our best.

18:26.020 --> 18:27.859
Sure, sure.

18:27.859 --> 18:28.419
Lawyer Xu,

18:28.419 --> 18:30.340
I think they're quite nice.

18:30.340 --> 18:31.820
Maybe I was overthinking earlier.

18:33.500 --> 18:34.419
Move!

18:43.340 --> 18:43.859
Lawyer Xu,

18:45.859 --> 18:46.899
I was indeed overthinking.

18:46.899 --> 18:47.740
Lawyer Xu,

18:49.899 --> 18:50.659
do you think

18:51.060 --> 18:52.300
I look like Ruan Yu?

18:53.820 --> 18:54.939
Lawyer Xu, you also feel something's off,

18:54.939 --> 18:55.500
right?

18:57.100 --> 18:57.500
So,

18:57.500 --> 18:58.540
what should we do?

19:01.020 --> 19:02.419
Should we switch back?

19:03.260 --> 19:04.619
I mean, how do we

19:04.619 --> 19:05.659
help them with the rice cake?

19:09.379 --> 19:11.020
You're doing pretty well.

19:11.419 --> 19:12.219
Thanks for your hard work.

19:12.740 --> 19:13.340
Miss Cai,

19:13.619 --> 19:14.219
if you have

19:14.219 --> 19:15.379
any legal questions,

19:15.379 --> 19:16.179
we'd be

19:16.500 --> 19:17.540
happy to help.

19:17.540 --> 19:18.859
But this physical work

19:18.859 --> 19:19.699
isn't really

19:19.699 --> 19:20.540
our job.

19:23.260 --> 19:23.980
See?

19:24.100 --> 19:25.179
They didn't run. Go!

19:25.500 --> 19:25.820
Go!

19:26.379 --> 19:27.179
Miss, auntie,

19:27.540 --> 19:28.540
Calm down.

19:29.060 --> 19:30.219
I've been thinking.

19:30.219 --> 19:32.139
If they are really accomplices,

19:32.379 --> 19:33.540
beating them again

19:33.540 --> 19:34.659
would only make things easier for them.

19:35.100 --> 19:36.100
What should we do then?

19:36.740 --> 19:37.659
Do you have a good idea?

19:38.740 --> 19:39.659
Since they say

19:39.659 --> 19:41.060
they consider us as family,

19:41.980 --> 19:43.100
we certainly won't refuse

19:43.100 --> 19:44.260
the kind help from our family.

19:45.340 --> 19:46.020
Yes, this...

19:46.020 --> 19:46.820
What do you mean?

19:46.820 --> 19:47.500
I don't get it.

19:47.859 --> 19:48.379
What?

19:49.219 --> 19:49.939
There must be

19:49.939 --> 19:50.659
a lot of work

19:50.659 --> 19:52.020
left undone before the New Year.

19:52.139 --> 19:52.659
Yeah.

19:53.820 --> 19:54.899
Then we don't need to be

19:55.179 --> 19:56.260
so polite to our family.

19:59.619 --> 20:01.139
What if they refuse?

20:01.340 --> 20:01.939
Then

20:04.780 --> 20:06.100
you can tell them

20:06.980 --> 20:07.619
Chen,

20:08.540 --> 20:10.060
you said

20:10.379 --> 20:11.659
we're like family.

20:11.980 --> 20:13.219
You just said it.

20:13.219 --> 20:14.580
But now you're backing out

20:15.100 --> 20:16.179
on such a small favor.

20:16.300 --> 20:17.459
How can we trust you?

20:17.459 --> 20:18.300
How could you?

20:18.300 --> 20:19.540
It's okay, it's okay.

20:19.780 --> 20:20.580
We're almost done

20:20.580 --> 20:21.500
anyway.

20:22.179 --> 20:23.419
There's still a lot left.

20:26.300 --> 20:26.780
Didn't you say

20:26.780 --> 20:28.060
that's all the rice cakes you have?

20:28.340 --> 20:30.540
Yes, that's all I have,

20:31.100 --> 20:31.939
but...

20:33.500 --> 20:34.179
What?

20:34.459 --> 20:35.820
Well,

20:36.260 --> 20:37.939
there are also

20:38.139 --> 20:38.859
some from my family.

20:39.540 --> 20:41.100
And from my family.

20:41.100 --> 20:43.260
And from my family.

20:43.260 --> 20:44.060
And from my family.

20:44.260 --> 20:45.100
These are all

20:45.419 --> 20:46.459
family.

20:46.459 --> 20:48.340
Shen'ao family.

20:48.500 --> 20:50.179
Yeah.

20:50.379 --> 20:51.540
Okay, you're family.

20:52.300 --> 20:53.619
I'm done.

20:54.060 --> 20:55.060
I quit.

20:55.659 --> 20:56.980
I think we're in an

20:56.980 --> 20:58.740
illegal employment relationship.

21:01.699 --> 21:02.300
Well,

21:02.780 --> 21:05.179
let's talk.

21:05.740 --> 21:06.500
Fine.

21:07.060 --> 21:07.899
They're in the wrong

21:07.899 --> 21:08.699
on their side.

21:09.179 --> 21:10.980
We're sure to win no matter how we talk.

21:11.260 --> 21:13.260
But that handsome guy

21:13.699 --> 21:14.939
is pretty eloquent.

21:15.260 --> 21:15.939
He said a lot of things

21:15.939 --> 21:17.100
we don't understand.

21:17.740 --> 21:19.219
Will we be fooled by him?

21:20.540 --> 21:21.500
Then let them

21:21.500 --> 21:22.340
send another person

21:22.340 --> 21:23.619
as a representative to talk with you.

21:23.619 --> 21:26.820
Will they agree?

21:27.139 --> 21:27.780
Yeah.

21:28.100 --> 21:29.859
Didn't you say that the person

21:29.859 --> 21:30.859
doesn't have a lawyer's certificate?

21:31.699 --> 21:32.740
Then tell them

21:32.820 --> 21:34.580
we only talk to people with certificates.

21:35.219 --> 21:35.820
Okay.

21:36.219 --> 21:37.619
I'll tell them later.

21:39.619 --> 21:41.100
If we can get the money back

21:41.100 --> 21:43.020
that the swindlers defrauded from the elderly,

21:43.179 --> 21:43.939
that would be great.

21:46.540 --> 21:47.260
How about this, Miss Cai.

21:48.100 --> 21:49.780
Let's keep in touch

21:50.100 --> 21:51.340
by using earphones.

21:51.619 --> 21:53.500
The more people, the better chance of winning.

21:57.619 --> 21:58.820
Lawyer Xu, are you okay?

21:59.139 --> 22:00.820
I'm fine. Just sit for a while.

22:02.820 --> 22:04.020
Why can't you

22:04.020 --> 22:05.219
go talk to them?

22:06.020 --> 22:06.459
They

22:06.459 --> 22:07.580
have made it clear that

22:07.899 --> 22:08.300
they only talk

22:08.300 --> 22:09.540
to someone with

22:09.540 --> 22:10.139
a lawyer's license.

22:12.580 --> 22:13.020
What if I can't

22:13.020 --> 22:14.219
reason with them?

22:21.699 --> 22:22.300
Take this.

22:23.780 --> 22:24.580
Contact by phone.

22:40.980 --> 22:41.820
This is too obvious. Here they come.

22:41.820 --> 22:42.500
Here they come.

22:42.619 --> 22:43.500
Let me take a look.

22:44.459 --> 22:45.419
Okay, take a look.

22:45.419 --> 22:46.060
Can you see it? It's okay.

22:46.060 --> 22:46.699
I can't see it. It's covered.

22:46.699 --> 22:47.379
It's covered.

22:54.060 --> 22:54.659
Hello, everyone.

22:55.500 --> 22:56.340
Sit, sit, sit.

22:56.820 --> 22:57.219
Okay.

23:06.419 --> 23:07.100
Listen.

23:08.139 --> 23:09.619
We don't reject

23:09.619 --> 23:11.020
voluntary work.

23:11.500 --> 23:12.300
But you've gone

23:12.300 --> 23:13.340
too far.

23:14.500 --> 23:15.459
If you think so,

23:15.780 --> 23:17.139
you can quit.

23:19.419 --> 23:20.619
Don't be led by them.

23:20.980 --> 23:22.139
Do you think there is

23:22.139 --> 23:23.219
any misunderstanding?

23:31.379 --> 23:32.179
Do I think there is

23:32.179 --> 23:33.100
any misunderstanding?

23:33.740 --> 23:35.340
We're here to provide legal aid.

23:35.619 --> 23:36.580
Our intention is to

23:36.580 --> 23:37.859
popularize legal knowledge.

23:38.419 --> 23:39.540
We are not fraudsters,

23:39.540 --> 23:40.540
and we will never do anything

23:40.540 --> 23:41.780
that is detrimental to you.

23:43.659 --> 23:44.980
They want to take the initiative.

23:45.659 --> 23:46.820
Then let's go along with them.

23:47.139 --> 23:48.300
Let them show their true colors first.

23:48.699 --> 23:49.859
We didn't say

23:50.699 --> 23:53.300
you are fraudsters.

23:54.619 --> 23:55.659
All who come are guests.

23:56.300 --> 23:57.659
We're all family here.

23:57.980 --> 23:58.859
Family?

23:59.580 --> 24:00.899
Well, your way of treating guests

24:00.899 --> 24:01.899
is quite unique.

24:02.219 --> 24:04.419
We don't treat you as outsiders.

24:04.939 --> 24:06.060
Alright, let's get down to business.

24:06.540 --> 24:07.419
We hope the neighborhood committee

24:07.419 --> 24:08.179
can help us

24:08.179 --> 24:09.379
promote legal aid,

24:09.379 --> 24:10.740
so that more local residents

24:10.740 --> 24:12.020
can understand the law.

24:12.459 --> 24:13.459
The neighborhood committee?

24:13.859 --> 24:15.459
What are you thinking?

24:15.659 --> 24:17.219
This is too much!

24:18.020 --> 24:18.820
You want the community committee

24:18.820 --> 24:20.219
to help you deceive people?

24:20.300 --> 24:21.459
What are you thinking?

24:21.740 --> 24:22.619
Really!

24:23.100 --> 24:23.780
Sure,

24:23.980 --> 24:24.939
we can help with the promotion.

24:24.939 --> 24:25.740
No problem.

24:25.740 --> 24:27.100
But we have one condition.

24:27.219 --> 24:28.300
What condition?

24:28.740 --> 24:30.619
Your former colleagues

24:31.020 --> 24:32.939
to return all the money

24:32.939 --> 24:35.100
they took from our town.

24:35.379 --> 24:36.939
Yes, all of it.

24:37.340 --> 24:38.340
We don't charge fees.

24:38.340 --> 24:39.820
Any charity that charges

24:39.820 --> 24:40.699
is a scam.

24:40.780 --> 24:41.939
If you've

24:41.939 --> 24:43.139
encountered this before,

24:43.139 --> 24:43.699
we're willing to

24:43.699 --> 24:44.780
provide legal aid.

24:44.780 --> 24:45.740
How can you prove

24:45.740 --> 24:46.899
you're not a scam?

24:47.500 --> 24:48.459
You can't prove

24:48.459 --> 24:49.419
we are frauds.

24:49.820 --> 24:50.379
But we can

24:50.379 --> 24:51.179
reasonably suspect.

24:51.500 --> 24:52.899
Suspecting also requires evidence.

24:52.899 --> 24:53.980
Otherwise, it's libel.

24:54.260 --> 24:55.780
We are libel?

24:56.139 --> 24:57.740
How dare you!

24:57.740 --> 24:58.500
Go away!

24:58.619 --> 24:59.020
Yeah.

24:59.020 --> 24:59.820
You are so unfair.

24:59.820 --> 25:00.980
-I'm telling you... -What?

25:00.980 --> 25:02.300
Today I must...

25:02.699 --> 25:03.699
You say I slandered you, right?

25:03.699 --> 25:04.379
Today I must...

25:04.379 --> 25:05.419
We are slanderers?

25:05.419 --> 25:06.139
-How can you talk like that?  -Yeah.

25:06.139 --> 25:06.980
You are so unfair.

25:06.980 --> 25:08.619
What? We are unfair?

25:08.619 --> 25:09.379
Who slandered you?

25:09.379 --> 25:10.179
Then you

25:10.260 --> 25:11.419
can deceive others everywhere?

25:11.419 --> 25:12.260
I... I'm telling you.

25:12.260 --> 25:13.659
You must make it clear today.

25:15.419 --> 25:16.219
Hello, Miss Cai.

25:18.139 --> 25:18.980
Hello, Miss Cai.

25:18.980 --> 25:19.699
Hello, Chen Hui.

25:20.060 --> 25:20.899
Hello, Chen Hui.

25:20.899 --> 25:21.500
Hello.

25:30.859 --> 25:31.619
Miss Cai, Ruan Yu.

25:38.500 --> 25:40.100
Lawyer Xu, what a coincidence.

25:40.859 --> 25:42.179
Yes, what a coincidence.

25:42.899 --> 25:45.780
We just come here to do charity.

26:10.060 --> 26:11.300
And there are some accidents.

26:12.939 --> 26:14.179
It can't be a coincidence.

26:14.820 --> 26:16.300
You are the two liars.

26:19.340 --> 26:20.419
I'm so sorry.

26:20.699 --> 26:22.219
I wronged you two lawyers.

26:22.699 --> 26:23.459
Never mind.

26:24.939 --> 26:26.939
Miss Cai, sometimes,

26:27.340 --> 26:28.980
the less like a liar a person is,

26:29.179 --> 26:30.699
the more likely he is to lie.

26:31.100 --> 26:31.899
So,

26:31.899 --> 26:33.260
it's a good thing

26:33.260 --> 26:34.020
to be more vigilant.

26:34.619 --> 26:35.939
I'm so sorry.

26:36.980 --> 26:38.219
But if you need anything,

26:38.459 --> 26:39.939
just tell me.

26:40.139 --> 26:41.820
Although we have everything in our town,

26:41.820 --> 26:43.740
it's not comparable to your big city.

26:44.179 --> 26:44.740
No, no, no.

26:44.740 --> 26:45.859
I'm afraid you're not used to it.

26:46.100 --> 26:47.899
Since Lawyer Xu is here for public welfare,

26:48.300 --> 26:49.619
you must be prepared.

26:50.219 --> 26:51.459
There is one thing I need.

26:52.500 --> 26:54.179
Miss Cai, I may have to trouble you.

26:54.580 --> 26:56.100
We are looking for a place to stay.

26:56.740 --> 26:57.859
That's easy.

26:59.540 --> 27:00.659
But I seem to have

27:00.980 --> 27:02.340
only one standard room left.

27:03.260 --> 27:04.020
Lawyer Xu, this...

27:05.179 --> 27:06.419
It's okay. It's good.

27:07.060 --> 27:07.619
Okay.

27:07.740 --> 27:08.980
I'll check you in now.

27:10.300 --> 27:10.780
Ms. Cai

27:11.379 --> 27:13.060
Well, there's one more thing.

27:14.300 --> 27:15.139
Can we get

27:15.139 --> 27:16.179
our clothes?

27:17.100 --> 27:17.500
This...

27:18.859 --> 27:19.740
No problem.

27:20.500 --> 27:21.139
Okay. Thank you.

27:21.139 --> 27:22.179
Okay. I'll go. Lawyer Xu.

27:22.179 --> 27:22.699
I'll go with you.

27:23.179 --> 27:23.859
Here, here, here.

27:24.580 --> 27:25.899
Barrister, have a seat.

27:26.179 --> 27:26.619
Okay.

27:47.580 --> 27:48.740
Don't you feel it?

27:48.939 --> 27:49.699
Miss Ruan

27:50.500 --> 27:51.939
knows this lawyer, doesn't she?

27:52.580 --> 27:54.179
Yeah, I think

27:54.340 --> 27:55.139
this lawyer

27:55.340 --> 27:56.139
has done something

27:56.139 --> 27:57.260
wrong to Miss Ruan.

27:58.020 --> 27:58.899
In my opinion,

27:59.100 --> 28:00.260
are they a couple

28:00.260 --> 28:01.100
having a fight?

28:01.100 --> 28:02.540
No way.

28:02.980 --> 28:06.379
Ms. Ruan is pretty

28:06.540 --> 28:07.740
and nice,

28:08.260 --> 28:09.260
and she's a great writer.

28:10.260 --> 28:11.419
The lawyer

28:12.699 --> 28:13.820
is just average-looking.

28:15.260 --> 28:16.419
I always feel

28:16.419 --> 28:17.820
he's not quite good enough

28:17.820 --> 28:18.859
for Ms. Ruan.

28:20.020 --> 28:20.820
I agree.

28:21.500 --> 28:22.699
That's it.

28:23.179 --> 28:23.939
You see,

28:24.139 --> 28:26.740
interesting soul is rare,

28:26.740 --> 28:27.780
but pretty face

28:27.780 --> 28:29.020
is everywhere.

28:30.419 --> 28:32.139
I heard two more liars came.

28:32.139 --> 28:33.619
-Let me see.  -Where are they?

28:35.100 --> 28:36.219
Everywhere?

28:37.060 --> 28:38.580
You're exaggerating.

28:39.020 --> 28:41.020
It's more pleasing to see a handsome guy.

28:41.379 --> 28:41.980
Yes.

28:42.459 --> 28:43.859
You're complimenting me.

28:44.340 --> 28:45.060
How do you know

28:45.060 --> 28:46.540
I just shaved today?

28:46.859 --> 28:48.219
You noticed?

28:50.340 --> 28:51.219
Let's go.

28:51.219 --> 28:51.899
Let's go.

28:53.699 --> 28:54.459
Where's the liar?

28:54.659 --> 28:55.379
Gone.

28:55.540 --> 28:56.500
Are you serious?

28:56.500 --> 28:57.780
Don't walk so fast.

28:57.939 --> 28:59.100
He's even blushing.

29:12.500 --> 29:13.820
Lawyer Xu, is it done?

29:14.500 --> 29:15.260
Okay, the clothes.

29:16.500 --> 29:17.020
OK.

29:17.659 --> 29:18.419
Miss Ruan, well,

29:18.419 --> 29:19.780
what a coincidence!

29:19.780 --> 29:20.859
I didn't expect to meet you here.

29:21.740 --> 29:23.899
Yeah, me neither.

29:24.379 --> 29:25.419
What a coincidence!

29:26.820 --> 29:28.459
Yeah, what a coincidence!

29:29.619 --> 29:30.340
Room card.

29:31.939 --> 29:33.260
Don't you want to talk to Miss Ruan?

29:34.139 --> 29:35.540
OK, I'll go first.

29:37.100 --> 29:37.540
OK.

29:39.179 --> 29:39.820
Lawyer Chen,

29:39.980 --> 29:40.859
I'll head back as well.

29:41.179 --> 29:42.139
Alright, Miss Ruan.

29:42.139 --> 29:43.100
We're staying over there.

29:43.340 --> 29:43.899
If you need anything,

29:43.899 --> 29:44.699
just come find us.

29:44.820 --> 29:45.260
And,

29:45.379 --> 29:46.060
where is the room?

29:46.780 --> 29:47.540
I didn't mention it earlier.

29:47.980 --> 29:48.580
It's over there.

29:48.580 --> 29:49.379
Sorry, Lawyer Xu.

29:49.379 --> 29:49.780
Over there.

29:49.859 --> 29:50.219
Alright.

29:50.580 --> 29:51.379
What are you waiting for?

29:51.899 --> 29:53.179
We've done a lot of research.

29:53.179 --> 29:53.980
Miss Ruan,

29:54.300 --> 29:55.379
come and join us.

29:55.619 --> 29:56.340
You go ahead.

29:56.659 --> 29:57.740
Okay, the luggage.

30:03.219 --> 30:03.820
How do you feel

30:04.100 --> 30:05.179
in a new environment?

30:05.179 --> 30:06.859
Do you feel refreshed?

30:07.219 --> 30:08.300
No.

30:09.379 --> 30:10.500
I just feel

30:10.619 --> 30:12.179
that I'm caught by fate,

30:12.740 --> 30:13.260
but still have to

30:13.260 --> 30:14.619
face it with tenacity.

30:15.260 --> 30:16.580
What a coincidence.

30:16.820 --> 30:17.500
Do you think he

30:17.500 --> 30:18.379
followed you on purpose?

30:19.540 --> 30:20.780
Why would he do that?

30:21.139 --> 30:22.340
To keep watching my embarrassment?

30:23.300 --> 30:23.939
Watching embarrassment

30:23.939 --> 30:25.219
isn't that addictive, is it?

30:26.379 --> 30:27.699
I think he's sincere this time.

30:27.699 --> 30:28.780
Maybe there's still hope.

30:30.859 --> 30:31.780
What's that noise over there?

30:32.300 --> 30:32.939
I think I heard

30:32.939 --> 30:33.899
Li Shican's song.

30:38.820 --> 30:39.859
It seems to be.

30:40.780 --> 30:42.020
I'll go check it out.

32:02.300 --> 32:02.899
Everyone,

32:04.100 --> 32:05.580
this is Shen'ao's Li Shican.

32:05.899 --> 32:07.980
I'm Li Shican.

32:11.939 --> 32:13.060
Where's the applause?

32:20.020 --> 32:22.300
I was on my way back from delivering goods,

32:22.619 --> 32:24.020
and I heard that a beautiful,

32:24.020 --> 32:25.820
generous,

32:25.820 --> 32:27.459
graceful, and lovely lady

32:27.939 --> 32:28.899
and two

32:30.619 --> 32:31.300
men.

32:32.020 --> 32:33.060
Now that I see you,

32:33.179 --> 32:34.219
I know it's true.

32:35.340 --> 32:36.060
Thank you.

32:36.060 --> 32:37.340
Is it that exaggerated, Lawyer Xu?

32:37.740 --> 32:38.939
You can smile.

32:39.899 --> 32:42.020
I know that my face

32:42.500 --> 32:43.699
can make people

32:43.699 --> 32:45.219
smile.

32:47.500 --> 32:48.020
Yes.

32:48.300 --> 32:50.459
Are you a fan of Li Shican?

32:51.340 --> 32:52.300
Not a fan.

32:52.939 --> 32:53.780
I'm a fish.

32:56.060 --> 32:56.780
That's an old joke.

32:56.780 --> 32:58.619
But you're a good mimic.

32:59.020 --> 32:59.619
Thank you.

32:59.780 --> 33:01.619
Fans are really something these days.

33:02.219 --> 33:04.899
Li Shishan, you went to the city.

33:05.100 --> 33:06.740
What did you do to my house?

33:06.740 --> 33:08.419
It's a mess!

33:08.980 --> 33:09.980
You, you...

33:09.980 --> 33:11.300
Take it all down!

33:11.580 --> 33:12.459
Gosh!

33:13.100 --> 33:14.379
I'm so sorry.

33:14.379 --> 33:15.260
This is my brother.

33:17.219 --> 33:20.580
Li Caiyue, you're embarrassing me again.

33:22.020 --> 33:23.419
I'm not just embarrassing you,

33:23.500 --> 33:24.580
I want to break your arm

33:24.580 --> 33:25.820
and leg.

33:26.500 --> 33:27.379
Would you do me the honor

33:27.379 --> 33:28.899
of inviting you to dinner?

33:29.699 --> 33:31.379
So cheesy.

33:31.659 --> 33:32.219
Go away.

33:32.419 --> 33:32.980
Go and drive away

33:32.980 --> 33:34.219
the car you parked at the door.

33:34.219 --> 33:34.939
What a shame.

33:36.419 --> 33:37.980
I'm so sorry.

33:38.500 --> 33:39.219
It's okay, Miss Cai.

33:39.580 --> 33:40.419
Don't mind.

33:40.500 --> 33:41.859
I happen to want to

33:41.859 --> 33:43.219
invite you to dinner.

33:43.980 --> 33:45.260
It's New Year's Eve.

33:45.780 --> 33:46.340
You can try

33:46.340 --> 33:47.300
the specialty dishes here.

33:47.419 --> 33:48.459
Let's celebrate together.

33:48.820 --> 33:49.540
Okay.

33:49.980 --> 33:50.780
Great.

33:51.139 --> 33:52.419
Please wait a moment.

33:52.740 --> 33:53.740
The food will be ready soon.

34:45.020 --> 34:48.259
Do you two know each other?

34:49.060 --> 34:49.619
Who?

34:51.940 --> 34:52.500
Her

34:54.020 --> 34:54.819
and him.

34:56.380 --> 34:57.179
Not you.

35:03.460 --> 35:06.219
I just observed you two

35:06.540 --> 35:08.259
for seven minutes and fifty-nine seconds.

35:09.100 --> 35:10.259
During this process,

35:10.980 --> 35:13.020
you didn't talk to him,

35:13.860 --> 35:15.940
and he didn't talk to you.

35:16.299 --> 35:17.699
But whenever

35:18.100 --> 35:19.500
your eyes

35:19.500 --> 35:20.500
met,

35:21.100 --> 35:22.619
it was like electricity.

35:22.779 --> 35:23.580
Zap!

35:24.380 --> 35:25.420
And you'd look away.

35:27.420 --> 35:29.179
So I'm curious,

35:30.020 --> 35:33.779
what's your deal?

35:36.819 --> 35:37.819
Nothing.

35:38.219 --> 35:38.900
No way.

35:40.380 --> 35:41.420
Look at this guy.

35:43.100 --> 35:45.020
Such a simple suit,

35:45.540 --> 35:46.540
he makes it

35:46.540 --> 35:48.020
look so elegant.

35:48.819 --> 35:49.500
It's like

35:49.500 --> 35:50.860
he's using minimal effort

35:50.980 --> 35:52.699
to look incredibly handsome.

35:53.219 --> 35:54.219
Even a super

35:54.219 --> 35:55.739
straightforward guy like me

35:55.900 --> 35:57.500
can't help but take a second glance.

35:59.819 --> 36:01.139
So, Great Writer Ruan,

36:01.299 --> 36:02.619
why is it that

36:03.179 --> 36:05.060
just a glance from him

36:05.380 --> 36:06.139
makes your eyes

36:06.139 --> 36:07.860
like you've been burned?

36:11.860 --> 36:12.860
You're so eloquent,

36:12.860 --> 36:13.699
why don't you talk about yourself?

36:16.900 --> 36:17.819
You...

36:20.940 --> 36:22.779
You're really good at eating apples.

36:26.900 --> 36:27.659
Shishan,

36:28.900 --> 36:29.900
you're so talented.

36:31.100 --> 36:32.179
It's a shame not to be a writer.

36:34.139 --> 36:35.020
Great Writer Ruan,

36:35.819 --> 36:36.980
to be honest,

36:37.779 --> 36:38.580
recently,

36:38.980 --> 36:40.739
I'm studying songwriting.

36:41.980 --> 36:42.940
I know.

36:43.299 --> 36:44.380
We're both creators.

36:44.380 --> 36:45.339
You understand me.

36:46.060 --> 36:47.940
Although I'm good at writing,

36:48.299 --> 36:49.299
I still get stuck

36:49.299 --> 36:50.179
in a rut.

36:50.860 --> 36:52.900
So I hope I can learn from you

36:52.900 --> 36:54.100
if I have time.

36:56.339 --> 36:57.619
I can't teach you.

36:58.420 --> 36:59.380
I'm here to collect materials

36:59.380 --> 37:00.540
because I can't

37:00.980 --> 37:02.500
come up with any ideas.

37:02.739 --> 37:04.219
What do you want to write?

37:07.739 --> 37:08.420
Romance.

37:08.779 --> 37:09.500
Romance?

37:13.179 --> 37:13.900
Don't you have

37:13.900 --> 37:15.420
a ready-made male lead?

37:18.940 --> 37:20.139
I'm willing to tell you

37:20.139 --> 37:20.940
my story.

37:25.460 --> 37:27.659
Yeah, after coming here,

37:28.060 --> 37:31.100
I feel my mind is bursting with ideas.

37:35.219 --> 37:35.860
By the way,

37:37.219 --> 37:39.139
what brand

37:39.500 --> 37:40.819
is your suit?

37:41.380 --> 37:42.339
It looks really cool.

37:42.619 --> 37:43.500
I bet it looks good

37:43.500 --> 37:44.500
on me too.

37:45.179 --> 37:45.940
Yours is nice too.

37:46.020 --> 37:47.259
It's a brand.

37:47.500 --> 37:48.940
The brand is called

37:49.500 --> 37:50.619
Paris...

37:51.139 --> 37:52.500
Li Caiyue,

37:53.100 --> 37:54.420
I have pride too.

37:55.500 --> 37:57.219
Try saying the full name again.

37:58.860 --> 37:59.860
Look at you two,

37:59.860 --> 38:01.339
talking nonsense here.

38:01.420 --> 38:02.699
Come on, it's time to eat.

38:02.860 --> 38:03.540
I made all my

38:03.540 --> 38:04.699
favorite dishes today.

38:04.699 --> 38:05.219
- I... - Come on.

38:05.219 --> 38:06.060
I don't want to hear it.

38:12.580 --> 38:13.139
Come on.

38:18.980 --> 38:20.580
Half an hour later is fine.

38:20.779 --> 38:21.380
How about this?

38:21.380 --> 38:21.940
Just have Wu

38:21.940 --> 38:23.420
send the case details

38:23.420 --> 38:24.779
to my email.

38:25.659 --> 38:26.380
Lawyer Xu,

38:27.339 --> 38:28.819
You guys are so busy.

38:29.179 --> 38:29.860
I was thinking of taking you

38:29.860 --> 38:31.100
to the night market later.

38:31.580 --> 38:32.179
Night market?

38:32.179 --> 38:33.060
Yeah, night market.

38:33.060 --> 38:34.420
Is it on that food street?

38:34.500 --> 38:35.540
Yeah, yeah.

38:35.819 --> 38:37.179
And it's not just food.

38:37.460 --> 38:38.500
There are also many local

38:38.500 --> 38:39.699
folk artists

38:39.699 --> 38:41.139
making handmade crafts.

38:41.139 --> 38:42.139
It's really interesting.

38:42.139 --> 38:42.699
Really?

38:42.699 --> 38:43.779
It's New Year's Eve today.

38:43.819 --> 38:44.980
It must be very lively.

38:45.900 --> 38:48.139
It's a pity that Lawyer Xu...

38:49.060 --> 38:49.940
Night market is good.

38:50.299 --> 38:51.139
I haven't been there.

38:51.819 --> 38:53.060
My work is easy to arrange.

38:53.779 --> 38:54.420
That's good.

38:55.179 --> 38:55.739
Let's go.

38:56.060 --> 38:56.699
Miss Cai

38:57.580 --> 38:58.619
You guys go.

38:58.619 --> 38:59.980
I'm a little tired today.

38:59.980 --> 39:01.020
I wanna go back to rest.

39:02.580 --> 39:03.179
You go.

39:05.540 --> 39:06.060
Well,

39:06.580 --> 39:07.460
well,

39:07.699 --> 39:08.779
the four of us go.

39:08.779 --> 39:10.540
I'll go too.

39:14.980 --> 39:15.739
Lawyer Xu, Lawyer Xu.

39:16.819 --> 39:17.500
I'm sorry.

39:17.500 --> 39:17.940
I forgot

39:17.940 --> 39:18.699
you were in a video conference.

39:18.699 --> 39:19.500
It's okay.

39:19.819 --> 39:20.819
I've finished.

39:21.380 --> 39:22.060
It's over, right?

39:22.219 --> 39:23.179
Let me tell you, Lawyer Xu,

39:23.179 --> 39:23.940
the night market here

39:23.940 --> 39:25.100
is really bustling.

39:25.100 --> 39:26.020
It's a shame that

39:26.020 --> 39:27.179
you and Miss Ruan didn't go.

39:31.139 --> 39:31.739
Alright.

39:34.139 --> 39:35.139
It's not that big of a shame.

39:35.139 --> 39:36.179
You were busy with work,

39:36.179 --> 39:37.259
and work is more important.

39:37.819 --> 39:38.619
There's a public legal consultation

39:38.619 --> 39:39.739
early tomorrow morning.

39:39.739 --> 39:41.299
I'm going upstairs to freshen up.

39:42.139 --> 39:42.659
Go ahead.

39:43.060 --> 39:43.580
Okay.

39:45.699 --> 39:46.860
[The boss is working,]

39:47.219 --> 39:48.500
[and I just got back from having fun.]

39:48.500 --> 39:49.619
[Now I'm going to freshen up again.]

39:50.420 --> 39:51.060
[Doesn't that make it seem like]

39:51.060 --> 39:52.739
[I have a problem with my work attitude?]

40:06.139 --> 40:07.139
Aren't you going to freshen up?

40:07.619 --> 40:08.699
I want to read a bit more.

40:08.699 --> 40:09.179
Lawyer Xu,

40:09.940 --> 40:10.420
have a seat.

40:10.659 --> 40:11.100
No, no.

40:11.100 --> 40:11.699
I won't disturb you.

40:11.699 --> 40:12.739
I can read here.

40:13.339 --> 40:14.219
I won't disturb you.

40:15.179 --> 40:15.739
Okay.

40:37.420 --> 40:38.380
If you are sleepy,

40:38.540 --> 40:39.699
just go back to sleep.

40:41.900 --> 40:42.420
I...

40:42.779 --> 40:43.540
I'm not sleepy.

40:43.540 --> 40:44.100
Lawyer Xu

40:44.219 --> 40:44.819
I'm not sleepy.

41:17.900 --> 41:18.540
Chen Hui

41:20.339 --> 41:20.940
Go upstairs.

41:21.860 --> 41:22.339
Lawyer Xu,

41:22.339 --> 41:23.299
maybe you should go up first.

41:23.299 --> 41:24.779
I'll study a bit longer.

41:26.380 --> 41:26.980
I'm sleepy.

41:34.980 --> 41:36.339
Let's go.

41:39.619 --> 41:40.819
Huai Shi, Happy New Year.

41:40.819 --> 41:41.619
Happy New Year.

41:42.179 --> 41:43.139
Am I not happy?

41:45.500 --> 41:47.339
The New Year's Eve fireworks this year

41:47.339 --> 41:48.900
are much better than last year's.

41:49.139 --> 41:51.299
Looks like the suggestions to the principal

41:51.299 --> 41:52.420
really made a difference.

41:52.819 --> 41:54.139
These photos are amazing!

41:55.460 --> 41:56.619
Which one do you think looks best?

41:57.940 --> 41:58.980
Which one do you like?

41:59.819 --> 42:00.819
They're all the same.

42:02.500 --> 42:04.540
How are they the same?

42:04.540 --> 42:05.060
Look,

42:05.060 --> 42:06.060
these two

42:06.139 --> 42:07.380
have different angles.

42:07.860 --> 42:08.819
And this one,

42:08.819 --> 42:10.380
the fireworks

42:10.380 --> 42:11.020
are different sizes.

42:11.020 --> 42:11.659
And this one.

42:11.779 --> 42:13.100
I brought that tree on purpose.

42:13.219 --> 42:14.020
Can't you see?

42:18.179 --> 42:19.339
Which one looks good?

42:19.619 --> 42:20.900
You look good.

42:21.940 --> 42:22.380
Forget it.

42:22.380 --> 42:23.219
You wouldn't understand anyway.

42:25.339 --> 42:27.339
You keep taking pictures.

42:27.699 --> 42:28.179
Can't you just

42:28.179 --> 42:29.619
enjoy the fireworks?

42:29.819 --> 42:30.860
Learn from your brother

42:32.420 --> 42:33.460
and Senior Ruan Yu.

42:50.860 --> 42:51.420
Brother,

42:52.139 --> 42:53.219
look at this firework.

42:54.020 --> 42:55.259
Does it remind you of the year

42:55.339 --> 42:57.179
when you held Sister Ruan Yu's hand?

43:12.739 --> 43:13.619
[Life is indeed full of]

43:13.619 --> 43:14.819
[humor and absurdity.]

43:15.980 --> 43:18.219
[Fortunately, time has finally slowed down.]

43:46.779 --> 43:48.139
[He was meticulous even in high school,]

43:48.619 --> 43:50.540
[wearing a white shirt for the big clean-up.]

43:51.540 --> 43:52.980
[Yet, over a decade later,]

43:53.580 --> 43:55.100
[he would be wearing ethnic attire,]

43:55.860 --> 43:57.299
[pounding rice cakes in a small town.]

43:58.779 --> 44:00.020
[I thought people like him]

44:00.540 --> 44:01.339
[would always be]

44:02.020 --> 44:02.900
[a refined]

44:02.900 --> 44:03.779
[and elite person.]

44:26.619 --> 44:27.659
[Although I was traumatized]

44:27.659 --> 44:28.619
[by the New Year's Eve,]

44:29.299 --> 44:30.179
[I didn't feel like]

44:30.500 --> 44:31.739
[going to the night market.]

44:32.940 --> 44:33.779
[But when I saw]

44:34.460 --> 44:35.900
[the meticulous him]

44:36.500 --> 44:38.540
[wearing a national costume]

44:39.060 --> 44:40.219
[and pounding rice cakes,]

44:44.139 --> 44:45.339
[I actually felt that this day]

44:46.020 --> 44:47.020
[was quite enjoyable.]

44:49.259 --> 44:50.179
[Maybe it's because]

44:50.500 --> 44:51.500
[I always made a fool of myself before,]

44:52.219 --> 44:54.259
[and he always stood above]

44:54.259 --> 44:55.179
[watching me make a fool of myself.]

44:56.219 --> 44:57.460
[Now the tables have turned,]

44:58.179 --> 45:00.460
[and I feel a bit better.]

45:03.659 --> 45:05.580
[Just a bit.]

45:11.420 --> 45:12.900
Lawyer Xu, do you think

45:12.900 --> 45:14.259
everyone will be too enthusiastic later?

45:14.500 --> 45:15.739
I've seen on TV that some legal aid

45:15.739 --> 45:16.699
they even send fruits

45:16.699 --> 45:17.619
and flowers.

45:17.900 --> 45:19.100
Will they send us too?

45:19.540 --> 45:21.100
No matter what they send,

45:21.259 --> 45:21.940
we can't accept it.

45:22.580 --> 45:23.420
Listen to me later.

45:24.779 --> 45:26.179
Okay, I'll keep order.

46:09.580 --> 46:11.219
I hope the communication skills I learned

46:11.699 --> 46:12.659
can help

46:12.659 --> 46:13.779
the two of them.
